{"tid":2491756,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"八達通領消費券 限額升至三千","createTime":"2021-04-16T14:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:13:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5e2b84e200256b6cc7e18072a2d3bb1c662692","tid":2491756,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/X3OPKMMW6JHNJI526WTKN5JWV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FX3OPKMMW6JHNJI526WTKN5JWV4%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLbzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=c22578d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FX3OPKMMW6JHNJI526WTKN5JWV4%2F&h=cf356695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/X3OPKMMW6JHNJI526WTKN5JWV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n八達通領消費券 限額升至三千<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/caGBZM7GKj7FD6tYlBqePG2k86U=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OEBYDMJ3LBD5TGVRB65V62OGKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcaGBZM7GKj7FD6tYlBqePG2k86U%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOEBYDMJ3LBD5TGVRB65V62OGKE.jpg&h=3d6dc99d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李玉兒<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府將透過AlipayHK、八達通、Tap &amp; Go拍住賞及WeChat Pay HK發放5,000元電子消費券，預料最快暑假開始接受登記，八達通公佈提升八達通儲值限額至3千元，方便市民使用消費劵。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：日日暢聚 一家族七人染疫  女患者拖4日才求醫 累50人送檢<br />\n<br />\n八達通營業及市務總監李玉兒表示，正研究經八達通服務站、交通補貼領取站、指定便利店和超級市場，以實體八達通卡領取消費券，或透過電子八達通卡領取。李玉兒說，在消費時不會分辨個人儲值金額和消費券，但可。。。。。。。。。。。。4月29日起，市民可經上述渠道，提升八達通儲值限額至3,000元，方便使用消費券。<br />\n<br />\n被問到假如有用戶將消費券金額由八達通卡，轉至八達通銀包，再轉到個人銀行戶口會如何處理、消費券餘額在到期日後會否自動消失，以及消費時會否優先扣除消費券金額等問題時，李玉兒則表示，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：恒基誓師大會 千人逼爆九展<br />\n<br />\n另外，為配合中小企參與，八達通表示。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料3,000商戶裝機<br />\n<br />\n至於eftPay則表示，因應電子消費券計劃，將。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\neftPay總經理黎萬信預料，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8091fa767c939a66d21a718863aeab236b9d266e","tid":2491756,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"八達通可以升限額3000好耐嘅事啦"}]}